### Invalid weighbridge ticket (negative weights)
POST http://localhost:8190/api/landside/weighbridge-ticket/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "licensePlate": "TRK-001",
  "grossWeight": -1000.0,
  "tareWeight": -500.0,
  "weighingTime": "31/08/2025 08:10"
}

### Invalid weighbridge ticket (tare weight greater than gross weight)
POST http://localhost:8190/api/landside/weighbridge-ticket/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "licensePlate": "TRK-001",
  "grossWeight": 10000.0,
  "tareWeight": 15000.0,
  "weighingTime": "31/08/2025 15:30"
}

